TOTVS Names Alexandre Dinkelman as Chief Financial Officer

-- B y   A d r i a n a   C h i a r i n i
-- 
2011-09-21T22:11:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/totvs-names-alexandre-dinkelman-as-chief-financial-officer.html
TOTVS SA (TOTS3)  said Alexandre Dinkelman
will take over as the company’s chief financial officer starting
Oct. 17 in a statement to the nation’s securities regulator
today. Dinkelman will also continue to serve as head of investor
relations, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adriana Chiarini in Rio de Janeiro at 
 achiarini4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jonathan Roeder at 
 jroeder@bloomberg.net  